

#### Delete a column
```python
# 3 Different alternatives
del myDF['columnName']
myDF.pop('columnName')
myDF = myDF.drop(['columnName'], axis=1)

# Multi delete
myDF = myDF.drop(['columnName', 'anotherName'], axis=1)

# By index
df.drop(df.columns[0], axis=1, inplace=True)

# Delete na values
df = df.dropna()

# Recalculate the index
df = df.reset_index(drop=True)
```

